####Clusters
There are various temporary and permanent clusters where bitcoin-friendly communities form. Temporary clusters are listed in [events](Bitcoin:Community_portal#Events).  Permanent communities include:

* [Free State Project](http://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=66832.0) New Hampshire
* [20 Mission](http://www.thebitcointrader.com/2012/05/bitcoins-hogwarts-san-francisco-tech.html) San Francisco, CA
* [Bitcoin Kiez](http://bitcoinmagazine.net/bitcoin-kiez-rollout-3-new-btc-accepting-stores-and-restaurants-in-berlin-more-to-come) Berlin, Germany

